 Porno For Pyros 在告别巡演前分享新单曲《Little Me》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/porno-for-pyros-share-new-single-little-me-ahead-of-farewell-tour-3581475?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=porno-for-火炮分享新单身小我提前告别之旅Anagricel DuranFri, 02 Feb 2024 20:00:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3581475 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Jane&#39;s Addiction 乐队的 Perry Farrell 于 2023 年 4 月 19 日在澳大利亚悉尼 Hordern Pavilion 演出。 （唐·阿诺德/WireImage 摄）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队将于本月晚些时候开始告别巡演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/porno-for-pyros-share-new-single-little-me-ahead-of-farewell-tour-3581475">Porno For Pyros 在告别巡演前分享新单曲《Little Me》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Jane&#39;s Addiction 乐队的 Perry Farrell 于 2023 年 4 月 19 日在澳大利亚悉尼 Hordern Pavilion 演出。 （唐·阿诺德/WireImage 摄）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Perry-Farrell-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/porno-for-pyros">Porno For Pyros</a>在即将举行的告别巡演之前分享了他们的最新单曲《Little Me》。</p><p> 《Little Me》是乐队之前发行的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/porno-for-pyros-announce-2024-farewell-tour-and-new-ep-3541341">Agua</a> 》之后的作品。这两首歌曲都将出现在乐队即将发行的 EP 中，该 EP 将于今年乐队巡演之前的某个时间发行。</p><p> <em>“嘿，嘿，哇哦/她说她有一个小我/不，不，别让我走/我带着你的小我，”主唱佩里·法雷尔（</em> <a href="/artists/perry-farrell">Perry Farrell）</a>用强劲的吉他连复段和绝妙的贝斯唱道线。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.songfacts.com/blog/interviews/peter-distefano-pyros" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Songfacts.com</em></a>采访时，吉他手 Peter DiStefano 解释了《Little Me》如何追溯到 90 年代，并说道：“Perry [Farrell] 当时有一个女朋友，他以为她怀孕了 — 他以为他会怀孕一个孩子。后来发现她并没有怀孕。这是一首情歌，但却是一首狂野的情歌。我喜欢吉他即兴演奏。” </p><p><iframe title="小我" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-_QPpus3erw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该乐队由迪斯蒂法诺、法雷尔和斯蒂芬·帕金斯组成，将于本月晚些时候开始在 16 个城市进行巡演。他们将于 2 月 13 日在加利福尼亚州圣安娜天文台开始巡演，并穿越美国。</p><p>此后，Porno For Pyros 将在洛杉矶、丹佛、芝加哥、多伦多、波士顿、纽约等地停留，然后于 3 月 10 日在新泽西州蒙特克莱尔的威尔蒙特剧院结束演出。粉丝们可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fporno-for-pyros-tickets%2Fartist%2F763399" target="_blank" rel="noopener">前往这里</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Czq8LexLHBJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1